test_even_range:
assert [8, 10, 12, 14, 16, 18] == [10, 12, 14, 16]
  At index 0 diff: 8 != 10
  Left contains 2 more items, first extra item: 16
  Full diff:
  - [10, 12, 14, 16]
  + [8, 10, 12, 14, 16, 18]
  ?  +++              ++++
test_large_range:
assert [4, 5, 6, 7, 8, 9] == [5, 6, 7, 8]
  At index 0 diff: 4 != 5
  Left contains 2 more items, first extra item: 8
  Full diff:
  - [5, 6, 7, 8]
  + [4, 5, 6, 7, 8, 9]
  ?  +++          +++
